'''巴亚克巴克'''（{{lang-en|Bāyakbāk}}），突厥人，生卒年不详，[[阿拔斯王朝|阿拔斯王朝]]官员，[[突伦王朝|突伦王朝]]建立者[[艾哈迈德·伊本·突伦|艾哈迈德·伊本·突伦]]的继父<ref name=islam>{{Cite book | author = Ann Katherine Swynford Lambton, Bernard Lewis | title = The Cambridge History of Islam: The Indian sub-continent, South-East Asia, Africa and the Muslim west, Volume 2 | location =  | publisher = Cambridge University Press | date = 1995 | pages = 178 | ISBN = 0521291356, 9780521291354 | accessdate = 2016-01-05 | url = https://books.google.com.hk/books?id=4AuJvd2Tyt8C&pg=PA178&dq=Bayakbak&hl=zh-CN&sa=X#v=onepage&q=Bayakbak&f=false | language = en | quote =  | archive-date = 2019-08-19 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20190819132630/https://books.google.com.hk/books?id=4AuJvd2Tyt8C&pg=PA178&dq=Bayakbak&hl=zh-CN&sa=X#v=onepage&q=Bayakbak&f=false | dead-url = no }}</ref>。曾获得由[[哈里发|哈里发]][[穆阿台兹|穆阿台兹]]赏赐的位于埃及的大片封地。<ref name=islam/>巴亚克巴克将对封地的有限管理权交由艾哈迈德·伊本·突伦。在巴亚克巴克被哈里发[[穆赫塔迪|穆赫塔迪]]下令杀死后，哈迈德·伊本·突伦完全接管了封地并在之后建立了[[突伦王朝|突伦王朝]]。<ref>{{Cite book | author = Reuben Levy | title = The Social Structure of Islam | location =  | publisher = CUP Archive | date = 1971 | pages = 536 | ISBN =  | accessdate = 2016-01-05 | url = https://books.google.com.hk/books?id=X-83AAAAIAAJ&pg=PA420&dq=Bayakbak&hl=zh-CN&sa=X#v=onepage&q=Bayakbak&f=false | language = en | quote =  | archive-date = 2019-08-15 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20190815204808/https://books.google.com.hk/books?id=X-83AAAAIAAJ&pg=PA420&dq=Bayakbak&hl=zh-CN&sa=X#v=onepage&q=Bayakbak&f=false | dead-url = no }}</ref>
